    {
      "para_id": "Q001951.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) When Enlil appointed Ninurta , his powerful warrior , as commissioner to Išme-Dagan , king of Sumer and Akkad , then ( Išme-Dagan ) fashioned the šita weapon , the fifty-headed mace for ( Ninurta ) , and displayed his beloved weapon on ( a platform of ) fired bricks for him ."
    }
  ],
